---
import Base from "@/layouts/Base.astro";
---

<Base
  title="Privacy Policy"
  meta_title="Privacy Policy — Australian Wedding Celebrants"
  description="Privacy policy for the Australian Wedding Celebrants website. We collect minimal personal information and do not use tracking technologies."
>
  <section class="py-16 md:py-20">
    <div class="container max-w-3xl">
      <h1 class="mb-4" style="font-weight: 700; letter-spacing: -0.44px;">
        Privacy Policy
      </h1>
      <p class="text-light text-sm mb-12" style="font-weight: 400;">
        Last updated: 23 April 2026
      </p>

      <div class="space-y-10 text-sm text-light" style="font-weight: 400; line-height: 1.7;">

        {/* 1 */}
        <div>
          <h2 class="text-base text-dark mb-3" style="font-weight: 600; letter-spacing: -0.18px;">1. Who we are</h2>
          <p>
            The website located at <strong>australianweddingcelebrants.com.au</strong> (the "Website") is owned and operated by <strong>Withers XYZ Pty Ltd</strong> as trustee for the <strong>Snow Withers Trust</strong>, ABN 37 709 073 991 ("we", "us", "our").
          </p>
          <p class="mt-3">
            We are committed to protecting your privacy in accordance with the <em>Privacy Act 1988</em> (Cth) and the Australian Privacy Principles (APPs). This Privacy Policy explains how we collect, use, disclose, and store personal information.
          </p>
          <p class="mt-3">
            You can contact us about privacy matters at <a href="mailto:hello@australianweddingcelebrants.com.au" class="text-dark underline">hello@australianweddingcelebrants.com.au</a>.
          </p>
        </div>

        {/* 2 */}
        <div>
          <h2 class="text-base text-dark mb-3" style="font-weight: 600; letter-spacing: -0.18px;">2. What personal information we collect</h2>
          <p>
            We collect only the personal information that you voluntarily provide to us. We do not use tracking codes, analytics scripts, advertising pixels, or similar tracking technologies on this Website. We do not use cookies for tracking purposes.
          </p>
          <p class="mt-3">
            The personal information we may collect includes:
          </p>

          <h3 class="text-sm text-dark mt-5 mb-2" style="font-weight: 600;">From website visitors (via the contact form)</h3>
          <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-1.5">
            <li>your name</li>
            <li>your email address</li>
            <li>the subject and content of your message</li>
          </ul>

          <h3 class="text-sm text-dark mt-5 mb-2" style="font-weight: 600;">From celebrants (via the listing application)</h3>
          <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-1.5">
            <li>your name and business name</li>
            <li>your email address</li>
            <li>your website URL and social media links</li>
            <li>your professional photo or logo</li>
            <li>your biography and service description</li>
            <li>your location and areas of service</li>
            <li>documentation submitted for tier verification, which may include insurance certificates, qualifications, review links, and statutory declarations</li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        {/* 3 */}
        <div>
          <h2 class="text-base text-dark mb-3" style="font-weight: 600; letter-spacing: -0.18px;">3. How we use your personal information</h2>
          <p>
            We use personal information only for the purposes for which it was collected:
          </p>
          <ul class="list-disc pl-6 mt-3 space-y-1.5">
            <li><strong>Contact form submissions:</strong> to respond to your enquiry or message.</li>
            <li><strong>Celebrant listing applications:</strong> to assess your application, create and maintain your directory listing, verify tier eligibility, and communicate with you about your listing.</li>
            <li><strong>Tier verification documents:</strong> to verify your eligibility for Endorsed or Luminary tier status. These documents are reviewed internally and are not published on the Website.</li>
          </ul>
          <p class="mt-3">
            We do not use your personal information for marketing, advertising, or profiling purposes. We do not sell, rent, or trade personal information to any third party.
          </p>
        </div>

        {/* 4 */}
        <div>
          <h2 class="text-base text-dark mb-3" style="font-weight: 600; letter-spacing: -0.18px;">4. How we store and protect your information</h2>
          <p>
            Personal information is stored using the following infrastructure:
          </p>
          <ul class="list-disc pl-6 mt-3 space-y-1.5">
            <li><strong>Contact form submissions</strong> are delivered to our email and processed via our form handling provider.</li>
            <li><strong>Celebrant listing data</strong> (names, descriptions, photos, and public profile information) is stored in a public Git repository on GitHub and published to the Website as static content. By submitting a listing, you consent to this information being made publicly available.</li>
            <li><strong>Authentication sessions and temporary data</strong> (magic link tokens, session tokens) are stored in Cloudflare KV with automatic expiry — magic links expire after 15 minutes and sessions after 24 hours.</li>
            <li><strong>Tier verification documents</strong> are stored in Cloudflare KV with a 90-day retention period, after which they are automatically deleted.</li>
            <li><strong>Images</strong> submitted with listings are processed (converted to WebP format) and stored as part of the Website's static content.</li>
          </ul>
          <p class="mt-3">
            We take reasonable steps to protect your personal information from misuse, interference, loss, unauthorised access, modification, and disclosure. However, no method of electronic storage or transmission is completely secure, and we cannot guarantee absolute security.
          </p>
        </div>

        {/* 5 */}
        <div>
          <h2 class="text-base text-dark mb-3" style="font-weight: 600; letter-spacing: -0.18px;">5. No tracking or analytics</h2>
          <p>
            This Website does not use:
          </p>
          <ul class="list-disc pl-6 mt-3 space-y-1.5">
            <li>Google Analytics or any other analytics platform</li>
            <li>Facebook Pixel, Google Ads, or any advertising tracking</li>
            <li>Third-party tracking cookies</li>
            <li>Fingerprinting or similar identification technologies</li>
          </ul>
          <p class="mt-3">
            Our hosting provider (Cloudflare) may collect basic server logs (such as IP addresses and request timestamps) as part of standard web infrastructure. We do not access or use this data for tracking individuals.
          </p>
        </div>

        {/* 6 */}
        <div>
          <h2 class="text-base text-dark mb-3" style="font-weight: 600; letter-spacing: -0.18px;">6. Use of AI in listing processing</h2>
          <p>
            When a celebrant submits a listing, we use AI (Anthropic's Claude API) to assist with editing the biography for grammar, generating an SEO-optimised meta title, and writing a third-person description. The information processed is limited to the content you submit with your listing (such as your name, bio, and location). This processing occurs on Anthropic's servers. We do not send your email address, authentication tokens, or tier verification documents to any AI service.
          </p>
        </div>

        {/* 6b — Agent and AI interfaces */}
        <div>
          <h2 class="text-base text-dark mb-3" style="font-weight: 600; letter-spacing: -0.18px;">6b. Agent and AI interfaces (MCP, A2A, ChatGPT apps)</h2>
          <p>
            The Website publishes several machine-readable surfaces so AI assistants and autonomous agents — including ChatGPT, Claude, Perplexity, and custom tools built by third parties — can read the directory and help couples find a celebrant. See <a href="/ai/" class="text-dark underline">/ai</a> for a plain-English overview.
          </p>

          <h3 class="text-sm text-dark mt-5 mb-2" style="font-weight: 600;">MCP server (read-only)</h3>
          <p>
            We operate a Model Context Protocol server at <code class="text-dark">api.australianweddingcelebrants.com.au/mcp</code>. It exposes read-only tools that search the directory, list celebrants by location or tier, and return a celebrant's full public profile. The server does not receive, store, or log any personal information about the person using the assistant — only the free-text query string, the requesting IP address, and standard Cloudflare request metadata. Queries are processed at the edge and responses are cached for up to 5 minutes; no conversation content from ChatGPT or any other assistant is sent to us.
          </p>

          <h3 class="text-sm text-dark mt-5 mb-2" style="font-weight: 600;">A2A enquiry relay</h3>
          <p>
            We operate an Agent-to-Agent endpoint at <code class="text-dark">api.australianweddingcelebrants.com.au/a2a</code> that lets an assistant acting on behalf of a couple relay a wedding enquiry to a specific celebrant by email. To use the <code class="text-dark">enquire_celebrant</code> skill, the assistant must supply:
          </p>
          <ul class="list-disc pl-6 mt-3 space-y-1.5">
            <li>the couple's names and email address (used solely as Reply-To on the email we send to the celebrant)</li>
            <li>the wedding date and location</li>
            <li>a short description of the ceremony</li>
            <li>the name of the assistant making the request</li>
          </ul>
          <p class="mt-3">
            We retain a log of each enquiry for 30 days in Cloudflare KV (celebrant slug, requesting IP, agent name, couple email, wedding date and location, plus a send timestamp and report-spam token) so a celebrant can flag the enquiry as spam if it's abusive. After 30 days the log expires automatically. We do not use enquiry data for marketing, analytics, or profiling, and we do not share it with any third party other than the celebrant the enquiry is being sent to.
          </p>
          <p class="mt-3">
            Celebrants can opt out of agent-relayed enquiries at any time by unchecking "Let AI agents relay wedding enquiries to my email address" on their listing edit page.
          </p>

          <h3 class="text-sm text-dark mt-5 mb-2" style="font-weight: 600;">Rate-limit counters</h3>
          <p>
            We maintain short-lived counters (keyed by requesting IP and celebrant slug) in Cloudflare KV to enforce the abuse limits described at <a href="/ai/" class="text-dark underline">/ai</a>. These counters expire after 24 hours. We do not retain raw IP addresses beyond the ban window of any celebrant who has reported spam (30 days).
          </p>

          <h3 class="text-sm text-dark mt-5 mb-2" style="font-weight: 600;">Content-Signal preferences</h3>
          <p>
            Our <code class="text-dark">robots.txt</code> publishes a Content-Signal directive of <code class="text-dark">ai-train=no, search=yes, ai-input=yes</code>. This asks compliant crawlers and AI platforms not to use celebrant biographies as training data, while still permitting search indexing and AI-assisted answers. Compliance with Content Signals is voluntary on the platform's side; this is a stated preference, not an enforceable technical measure.
          </p>
        </div>

        {/* 7 */}
        <div>
          <h2 class="text-base text-dark mb-3" style="font-weight: 600; letter-spacing: -0.18px;">7. Disclosure of personal information</h2>
          <p>
            We may disclose personal information to:
          </p>
          <ul class="list-disc pl-6 mt-3 space-y-1.5">
            <li><strong>Service providers</strong> who assist in operating the Website — including Cloudflare (hosting, edge computing, and storage), Netlify (static site hosting), GitHub (code and content hosting), and Anthropic (AI text processing). These providers may process data on servers located outside Australia, including in the United States.</li>
            <li><strong>Law enforcement or regulatory bodies</strong> where required or authorised by Australian law.</li>
          </ul>
          <p class="mt-3">
            Published celebrant listings (names, photos, descriptions, websites, and locations) are publicly accessible on the Website and may be indexed by search engines and accessed by AI systems. This is the intended purpose of the directory.
          </p>
        </div>

        {/* 8 */}
        <div>
          <h2 class="text-base text-dark mb-3" style="font-weight: 600; letter-spacing: -0.18px;">8. Overseas disclosure</h2>
          <p>
            Some of our service providers operate in or have servers located in countries outside Australia, including the United States. By using this Website or submitting information to us, you consent to the disclosure of your personal information to overseas recipients in accordance with APP 8. We take reasonable steps to ensure that overseas recipients handle your personal information in accordance with the APPs.
          </p>
        </div>

        {/* 9 */}
        <div>
          <h2 class="text-base text-dark mb-3" style="font-weight: 600; letter-spacing: -0.18px;">9. Your rights</h2>
          <p>
            Under the Australian Privacy Principles, you have the right to:
          </p>
          <ul class="list-disc pl-6 mt-3 space-y-1.5">
            <li><strong>Access</strong> the personal information we hold about you.</li>
            <li><strong>Request correction</strong> of any personal information that is inaccurate, out of date, incomplete, irrelevant, or misleading.</li>
            <li><strong>Request deletion</strong> of your personal information, subject to any legal obligations we may have to retain it.</li>
            <li><strong>Request removal</strong> of your celebrant listing at any time.</li>
          </ul>
          <p class="mt-3">
            To exercise any of these rights, contact us at <a href="mailto:hello@australianweddingcelebrants.com.au" class="text-dark underline">hello@australianweddingcelebrants.com.au</a>. We will respond to your request within 30 days.
          </p>
        </div>

        {/* 10 */}
        <div>
          <h2 class="text-base text-dark mb-3" style="font-weight: 600; letter-spacing: -0.18px;">10. Children's privacy</h2>
          <p>
            This Website is not directed at children under 18 years of age. We do not knowingly collect personal information from children. If you believe we have inadvertently collected information from a child, please contact us and we will delete it promptly.
          </p>
        </div>

        {/* 11 */}
        <div>
          <h2 class="text-base text-dark mb-3" style="font-weight: 600; letter-spacing: -0.18px;">11. Changes to this Privacy Policy</h2>
          <p>
            We may update this Privacy Policy from time to time. The "Last updated" date at the top of this page will reflect any changes. We encourage you to review this page periodically. Your continued use of the Website after changes are posted constitutes acceptance of the revised policy.
          </p>
        </div>

        {/* 12 */}
        <div>
          <h2 class="text-base text-dark mb-3" style="font-weight: 600; letter-spacing: -0.18px;">12. Complaints</h2>
          <p>
            If you believe we have breached the Australian Privacy Principles, please contact us at <a href="mailto:hello@australianweddingcelebrants.com.au" class="text-dark underline">hello@australianweddingcelebrants.com.au</a> and we will investigate your complaint promptly.
          </p>
          <p class="mt-3">
            If you are not satisfied with our response, you may lodge a complaint with the <strong>Office of the Australian Information Commissioner (OAIC)</strong> at <a href="https://www.oaic.gov.au" class="text-dark underline" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">www.oaic.gov.au</a> or by calling 1300 363 992.
          </p>
        </div>

        {/* 13 */}
        <div>
          <h2 class="text-base text-dark mb-3" style="font-weight: 600; letter-spacing: -0.18px;">13. Contact</h2>
          <p>
            For any privacy-related questions or requests, please contact:
          </p>
          <div class="mt-3 rounded-card p-6 border border-border bg-theme-light">
            <p class="text-dark" style="font-weight: 500;">Withers XYZ Pty Ltd as trustee for the Snow Withers Trust</p>
            <p class="mt-1">ABN 37 709 073 991</p>
            <p class="mt-1">Email: <a href="mailto:hello@australianweddingcelebrants.com.au" class="text-dark underline">hello@australianweddingcelebrants.com.au</a></p>
          </div>
        </div>

      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Base>
